00:28:13.859 --> 00:28:16.654
Your mother and father are cool.

00:28:19.573 --> 00:28:20.658
I'll accept your leave.

00:28:21.617 --> 00:28:23.702
But promise me you'll return.

00:28:25.121 --> 00:28:26.122
Thank you.

00:28:26.205 --> 00:28:27.206
Jeez.

00:28:28.290 --> 00:28:30.209
This is why I don't get in a relationship.

00:28:32.002 --> 00:28:34.130
Even if it flops like mine,
it's still worth it.

00:28:34.213 --> 00:28:38.050
That's why you should've dated me,
you idiot.

00:28:38.134 --> 00:28:40.219
There you go again.

