Why? Are you going to marry another woman?

00:39:18.440 --> 00:39:19.274
What?

00:39:20.317 --> 00:39:23.111
No, but it's not like
we're getting married now.

00:39:23.195 --> 00:39:24.029
This is pretty.

00:39:32.079 --> 00:39:34.414
Ta-da.

00:39:37.918 --> 00:39:39.002
Let's take a picture.

00:39:40.087 --> 00:39:41.922
What? Okay.

00:39:43.632 --> 00:39:44.716
Hurry up.

00:39:46.551 --> 00:39:47.844
Why are you smiling like that?

00:39:47.928 --> 00:39:48.762
What?

00:39:50.806 --> 00:39:53.642
Let's try again. One, two, three.

00:39:55.268 --> 00:39:57.604
Ji-woo, you look so beautiful.

00:39:58.355 --> 00:39:59.189
Let me.

00:39:59.272 --> 00:40:00.732
Thanks. Thank you.

00:40:01.399 --> 00:40:03.193
Okay, smile.

00:40:03.819 --> 00:40:07.405
Ready. One, two, three.

00:40:07.489 --> 00:40:08.615
One more?

00:40:11.326 --> 00:40:12.577
Okay, smile.

